<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v5" title="Q28_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceD</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En la siguiente ficha se indican las dosis de un medicamento para perros:<br />Dosis recomendada: <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> gotas por cada <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> kg de peso del perro.</p>
    <p>Se quiere medicar a un perro que pesa <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> kg.</p>
    <p>Si se mantiene la misma proporción indicada en la ficha, ¿cuántas gotas se deben administrar a este perro?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>&#160;gotas</m:mo><m:mo>&#160;corresponden&#160;a&#160;</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>&#160;kg</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, no a <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> kg. Manteniendo la proporción, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> gotas no satisfacen el problema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si fueran <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> gotas para <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> kg, la razón sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> gota por kg. Pero la ficha indica <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> gotas por kg. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> gotas no mantienen la proporción.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math> gotas para <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> kg, la razón sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> gotas por kg. La ficha indica <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> gotas por kg. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math> gotas no corresponden a la misma proporción. El cálculo correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se mantiene la proporción de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>&#160;gotas&#160;por&#160;</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>&#160;kg</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Para <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> kg, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, se deben administrar <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:math> gotas.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso por proporcionalidad</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la proporción dada</strong></p>
            <p>La ficha indica que se administran <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> gotas por cada <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> kg.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Plantear el cálculo para 10 kg</strong></p>
            <p>Como se mantiene la misma proporción, multiplicamos las gotas por el nuevo peso y dividimos por el peso de referencia:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Resolver la operación</strong></p>
            <p>Primero,</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Luego,</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Si el perro pesa <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> kg, se deben administrar <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:math> gotas.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>D</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>